<p>Hello, <%= @resource.name %>!</p>

<p>We received a request to send you a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] + edit_password_path(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token) %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>

<p>
  Thanks for huddling up with your team!
  <br />&nbsp;
  -- Your HuddleUp team
</p>

